<script>
import { watch } from '@vue/runtime-core';
export default {
    props:  {
        user:{
            type: Object,
            require: true
        },role:{
            type: String,
            require: true
        }

    },
    setup(props) {
        watch(()=> props.role , ()=>{
            if (props.role == 'student'){
                document.getElementById('card').classList.add("student-theme")
            }
            else if (props.role == 'teacher'){
                document.getElementById('card').classList.remove("student-theme")
            }
        } ,)
        return {
        };
    },
};
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>

.student-theme{
    --color1: rgb(255, 102, 0) !important;
    --color2: rgb(255, 167, 66) !important;
}
#card {
    --color1: var(--secondary-color-dark);
    --color2: var(--secondary-color-normal);
    max-width: 100%;
    max-height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    .text {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        color: #000;
    }
}

.text-label {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-family: MalgunGothic-Semilight, Malgun Gothic;
    font-weight: 400;
}
.text-info {
    font-size: 15px;

    font-weight: 300;
}

.small {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 800;
    fill: #fff;
}

.big {
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 30px;
    fill: #fff;
}

.big-2 {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 15px;
    fill: #303030;
}

.cls-1 {
    isolation: isolate;
}

.cls-2 {
    opacity: 0.19;
}

.cls-10,
.cls-2,
.cls-6 {
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
}

.cls-3 {
    transition: .5s fill;
    fill: var(--color1);
}

.cls-4 {
    transition: .5s fill;
    fill: var(--color2);
}

.cls-5 {
    fill: #fff;
}

.cls-6 {
    opacity: 0.25;
}

.cls-7 {
    fill: #fff;
    font-size: 17px;
